data.description: Welcome to this charming corner lot home that offers both comfort and style. This inviting residence features three spacious bedrooms, providing ample space for relaxation and privacy. The master suite boasts a private en-suite bathroom, creating a serene retreat within your own home. The open-concept living area is perfect for entertaining, with a well-appointed kitchen that flows seamlessly into the dining and living spaces. The heart of the home is undoubtedly the cozy fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere during chilly evenings. The corner lot location enhances the curb appeal and provides additional outdoor space, offering endless possibilities for landscaping and outdoor activities. This home is not just a place to live; it's a haven where memories are made. Explore the comfort, functionality, and charm that this corner lot gem has to offer. Welcome home!
